Revision history for Perl extension Ridge.

0.11  Mon Jun 25 2012
      - Support HTTP HEAD request method
      - Support HTTP 204 No-Content response code
      - Support Plack 0.9983 and later
      - Fix content-type of JSONP
      - Support custom subclass of Ridge::Request/Response
      - Support per-device templates
      - Add Ridge::Request#original_uri

